[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Here is the <st data-num=\"02377\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">about</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> was <st data-num=\"02372\" class=\"\">revealed</st> to <st data-num=\"03470\" class=\"\">Isaiah</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"0531\" class=\"\">Amoz</st> during the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> when <st data-num=\"05818\" class=\"\">Uzziah</st>, <st data-num=\"03147\" class=\"\">Jotham</st>, <st data-num=\"0271\" class=\"\">Ahaz</st>, and <st data-num=\"03169\">Hezekiah</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">reigned over</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen</st>, O <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heavens</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0238\" class=\"\">pay attention</st>, O <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">speaks</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">raised</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> I <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">brought</st> them <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">up</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">they</st> have <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">rebelled</st><n id=\"5\" /> against me!</p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">An <st data-num=\"07794\" class=\"\">ox</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">recognizes</st> its <st data-num=\"07069\" class=\"\">owner</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"02543\" class=\"\">donkey</st> recognizes <st data-num=\"018\" class=\"\">where</st> its <st data-num=\"01167\" class=\"\">owner</st> <st data-num=\"018\" class=\"\">puts</st> its <st data-num=\"018\" class=\"\">food</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">recognize</st> me,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understand</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01945\">Beware</st> <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinful</st> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"03515\" class=\"\">weighed down</st> by <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">evil deeds</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They are <st data-num=\"02233\" class=\"\">offspring</st> who <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">do wrong</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st><n id=\"2\" /> who <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">do wicked things</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They have <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandoned</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"05006\" class=\"\">rejected</st> the <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">Holy One</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They are <st data-num=\"02114\" class=\"\">alienated</st> <st data-num=\"0268\" class=\"\">from</st> him.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921 04100\">Why</st> do you <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">insist on</st> being <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">battered</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Why do you <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">continue</st> to <st data-num=\"05627\" class=\"\">rebel</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st> has a <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">massive</st> <st data-num=\"02483\" class=\"\">wound</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">your <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"03824\">heart</st> is <st data-num=\"01742\">sick</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">From the <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">soles</st> of your <st data-num=\"07272\" class=\"\">feet</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> your <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there is no</st> <st data-num=\"04974\">spot that is unharmed</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">There are only <st data-num=\"06482\" class=\"\">bruises</st>, <st data-num=\"02250\" class=\"\">cuts</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"02961\" class=\"\">open</st> <st data-num=\"04347\" class=\"\">wounds</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> been <st data-num=\"02115\" class=\"\">cleansed</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"02280\" class=\"\">bandaged</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">nor</st> have they been <st data-num=\"07401\" class=\"\">treated</st><n id=\"3\" /> with <st data-num=\"08081\" class=\"\">olive oil</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> is <st data-num=\"08077\" class=\"\">devastated</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">your <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> <st data-num=\"08313\" class=\"\">burned</st> with <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">Right before</st> your <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">eyes</st> your <st data-num=\"0127\" class=\"\">crops</st><p class=\"poetry\">are being <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> by <st data-num=\"02114\" class=\"\">foreign invaders</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02114\" class=\"\">They</st> leave behind <st data-num=\"08077\" class=\"\">devastation</st> and <st data-num=\"02114\" class=\"\">destruction</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st><n id=\"1\" /> is <st data-num=\"03498\" class=\"\">left</st> isolated,<p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"05521\" class=\"\">hut</st> in a <st data-num=\"03754\" class=\"\">vineyard</st><p class=\"poetry\">or a <st data-num=\"04412\" class=\"\">shelter</st> in a <st data-num=\"04750\" class=\"\">cucumber field</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">she is a <st data-num=\"05341\" class=\"\">besieged</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03884\" class=\"\">If</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st><n id=\"1\" /> had not <st data-num=\"03498\" class=\"\">left</st> us a <st data-num=\"08300\">few survivors</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">we would have <st data-num=\"04592\">quickly</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">been</st> like <st data-num=\"05467\" class=\"\">Sodom</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">we would have <st data-num=\"01819\" class=\"\">become like</st> <st data-num=\"06017\" class=\"\">Gomorrah</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"07101\" class=\"\">leaders</st> of <st data-num=\"05467\" class=\"\">Sodom</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0238\" class=\"\">Pay attention</st> to our <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">rebuke</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"06017\" class=\"\">Gomorrah</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cOf <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what importance</st> to me are your <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st>?\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI have <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">had</st> my <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">fill</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">of <st data-num=\"0352\" class=\"\">rams</st> and the <st data-num=\"02459\" class=\"\">fat</st> from <st data-num=\"04806\" class=\"\">steers</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st> of <st data-num=\"06499\" class=\"\">bulls</st>, <st data-num=\"03532\" class=\"\">lambs</st>, and <st data-num=\"06260\" class=\"\">goats</st><p class=\"poetry\">I do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02654\" class=\"\">want</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">When</st> you <st data-num=\"0935 07200\">enter</st> my <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">presence</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310 01245 03027\">do you actually think I want</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">animals <st data-num=\"07429\" class=\"\">trampling</st> on my <st data-num=\"02691\" class=\"\">courtyards</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> any <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">more</st> <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">meaningless</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04503\" class=\"\">offerings</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I consider your <st data-num=\"07004\" class=\"\">incense</st> <st data-num=\"08441\" class=\"\">detestable</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">You observe <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">new moon festivals</st>, <st data-num=\"07676\" class=\"\">Sabbaths</st>, and <st data-num=\"07121 04744\">convocations</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but I <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"03201\" class=\"\">tolerate</st> <st data-num=\"0205\" class=\"\">sin-stained</st> <st data-num=\"06116\" class=\"\">celebrations</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"08130\" class=\"\">hate</st> your <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">new moon festivals</st> and <st data-num=\"04150\" class=\"\">assemblies</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"01961 05921\">are</st> a <st data-num=\"02960\" class=\"\">burden</st><p class=\"poetry\">that I <st data-num=\"03811\">am tired</st> of <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">carrying</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">When you <st data-num=\"06566\" class=\"\">spread out</st> your <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">hands</st> in prayer,<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"05956 05869\">look</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">the other way</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">when</st> you <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">offer</st> your <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"08605\" class=\"\">prayers</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">I do <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen</st><p class=\"poetry\">because your <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st> are <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">covered</st> with <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07364\" class=\"\">Wash</st>! <st data-num=\"02135\" class=\"\">Cleanse</st> yourselves!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">Remove</st> your <st data-num=\"07455\" class=\"\">sinful</st> <st data-num=\"04611\" class=\"\">deeds</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">from</st> my <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">sight</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02308\" class=\"\">Stop</st> <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">sinning</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03925\" class=\"\">Learn</st> to <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">do what is right</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">Promote</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">Give</st> the <st data-num=\"02556\" class=\"\">oppressed</st> <st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">reason to celebrate</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">Take up the cause of</st> the <st data-num=\"03490\" class=\"\">orphan</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07378\" class=\"\">Defend the rights of</st> the <st data-num=\"0490\" class=\"\">widow</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\"><n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Come</st>, let\u2019s <st data-num=\"03198\" class=\"\">consider</st> your <st data-num=\"03198\" class=\"\">options</st>,\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Though</st> your <st data-num=\"02399\" class=\"\">sins</st> have <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">stained</st> you like the color <st data-num=\"08144\" class=\"\">red</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">you can <st data-num=\"03835\" class=\"\">become white</st><n id=\"3\" /> like <st data-num=\"07950\" class=\"\">snow</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">though</st> they <st data-num=\"0119\" class=\"\">are as easy to see</st> as the color <st data-num=\"08438\" class=\"\">scarlet</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">you can <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st><n id=\"4\" /> white like <st data-num=\"06785\" class=\"\">wool</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> you <st data-num=\"014\" class=\"\">have a willing attitude</st> and <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">obey</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">then you will again <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st> the <st data-num=\"02898\" class=\"\">good</st> crops of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">if</st> you <st data-num=\"03985\" class=\"\">refuse</st> and <st data-num=\"04784\" class=\"\">rebel</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">you will be <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">devoured</st><n id=\"1\" /> by the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>.\u201d<p class=\"poetry\">Know <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for certain</st> that the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"06310 03068\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">spoken</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">How</st> tragic that the <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">once-faithful</st> <st data-num=\"07151\" class=\"\">city</st><p class=\"poetry\">has <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> a <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">prostitute</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">She <st data-num=\"04395\" class=\"\">was</st> once <st data-num=\"04395\">a center</st> of<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06664\" class=\"\">fairness</st> <st data-num=\"03885\" class=\"\">resided</st> in her\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">but <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> only <st data-num=\"07523\" class=\"\">murderers</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st> has <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> <st data-num=\"05509\" class=\"\">scum</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">your <st data-num=\"05435\" class=\"\">beer</st> is <st data-num=\"04107\" class=\"\">diluted</st> with <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st> are <st data-num=\"05637\" class=\"\">rebels</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"02270\" class=\"\">associate</st> with<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"01590\" class=\"\">thieves</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> of them <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">love</st> <st data-num=\"07810\" class=\"\">bribery</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07291\" class=\"\">look for</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"08021\" class=\"\">payoffs</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">take up the cause of</st> the <st data-num=\"03490\" class=\"\">orphan</st><n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"0935 0413\">defend</st> the <st data-num=\"07379\" class=\"\">rights</st> of the <st data-num=\"0490\" class=\"\">widow</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">Therefore</st>, the <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"046\" class=\"\">Powerful One</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says this</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"01945\" class=\"\">Ah</st>, I will <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">seek vengeance</st><n id=\"3\" /> against my <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">adversaries</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05358\" class=\"\">take revenge</st> against my <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07725 03027 05921\">attack</st> you;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">purify</st> your <st data-num=\"05509\" class=\"\">metal</st> with <st data-num=\"01253\">flux</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">remove</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> your <st data-num=\"0913\" class=\"\">slag</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">reestablish</st> honest <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">judges</st> as in <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">former times</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">wise <st data-num=\"03289\" class=\"\">advisers</st> as in <st data-num=\"08462\" class=\"\">earlier days</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0310 03651\">Then</st> you will be <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">called</st>, \u2018The <st data-num=\"06664\" class=\"\">Just</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">City</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">Faithful</st> <st data-num=\"07151\" class=\"\">Town</st>.\u2019\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st> will be <st data-num=\"06299\" class=\"\">freed</st> by <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and her <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">returnees</st> by <st data-num=\"06666\" class=\"\">righteousness</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">All</st> <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">rebellious</st> <st data-num=\"02400\" class=\"\">sinners</st> will be <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">shattered</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">those who <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandon</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">perish</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, they<n id=\"1\" /> will be <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">ashamed</st> of the <st data-num=\"0352\" class=\"\">sacred trees</st><p class=\"poetry\">you<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"02530\">find</st> so <st data-num=\"02530\">desirable</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">you will be <st data-num=\"02659\" class=\"\">embarrassed</st> because of the <st data-num=\"01593\" class=\"\">sacred orchards</st><n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">where</st> you <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">choose</st> to worship.</p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> you will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> like a <st data-num=\"0424\" class=\"\">tree</st> whose <st data-num=\"05929\" class=\"\">leaves</st> <st data-num=\"05034\" class=\"\">wither</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">like an <st data-num=\"01593\" class=\"\">orchard</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"04325 0369\">is unwatered</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "30"
