    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02634\" class=\"\">powerful</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> like<n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"05296\" class=\"\">thread of yarn</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"06467\" class=\"\">deeds</st> like a <st data-num=\"05213\" class=\"\">spark</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">both</st> will <st data-num=\"01197\" class=\"\">burn</st> <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">together</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> one will <st data-num=\"03518\" class=\"\">put out the fire</st>. </p>",
